description: Never add code comments when developing
alwaysApply: true
---

# No comments in code

- Do not write comments in source code (`//`, `/* */`, `{/* */}`, JSDoc, or HTML comments).
- Do not add new comments when creating or editing files.
- Prefer clear names and structure over explanatory comments.
- Triple-slash directives like `/// <reference ... />` may remain when required by the toolchain.
